  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GunDeck[100] is a twin-stick shooter where the aim of the game is to conquer 100 levels of bullet hell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Amass a ring of guns and blow off fireworks of elemental crystals that come in your choice of corrosive acid, freezing ice, eagle-eye homing, replicating magic, and sledge-hammer blight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After each wave, choose from three dealt cards to add to your growing deck. But choose wisely! These cards will grant you new weapons, power up your shots, earn you companions, curse your enemies— or even curse you! (For a fair trade, of course…) Build yourself a powerful gun deck, or regret it when you meet…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >…the ten big bad bosses that stand between you and the eponymous level. Not only do you get your pick of extra special cards for defeating them, you’ll earn yourself new ships with built-in features that change the way you play entirely. (One Gun Run, anyone?)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> <br>- Hundreds of perks to choose from <br>- Unique perks after boss waves <br>- Loads of steam achievements <br>- Multiplayer local co-op! <br> <br><strong>Classic (A Side):</strong>  <br>- 100 wicked waves.  <br>- 10 bad bosses.  <br>- 10 unlockable alternate ships that change the way the game is played.  <br> <br><strong>Classic (B Side):</strong>  <br>- 100 additional waves.  <br>- 10 more bosses.  <br>- Additional unlockable buffs for the 10 base ships.  <br> <br><strong>Infinity:</strong>  <br>- No cap on number of waves.  <br>- Compete for top spot in leaderboard.  <br>- 5 additional unlockable ships.  <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/48a4adb1af6e37da0c885c9b648f8b12.poster.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/48a4adb1af6e37da0c885c9b648f8b12.webm?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/48a4adb1af6e37da0c885c9b648f8b12.mp4?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PICK YOUR PERKS</strong><br>Choosing from hundreds of cards makes every run a completely different experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/7f20011b62fd045be78af3a0fe3ff9fd.poster.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/7f20011b62fd045be78af3a0fe3ff9fd.webm?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/7f20011b62fd045be78af3a0fe3ff9fd.mp4?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BUILD YOUR ARSENAL</strong> <br>Pick up gun cards, to add guns to your stack. Your ship will fire through your entire stack before reloading. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/b75f2dab46c27042d1fc042ec2787ddc.poster.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/b75f2dab46c27042d1fc042ec2787ddc.webm?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/b75f2dab46c27042d1fc042ec2787ddc.mp4?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FIGHT YOUR FOES</strong><br>Dozens of unique enemies square off with you, each with their own vile volleys. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/aa8662d32c64e10db4d0726e75762f32.poster.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/aa8662d32c64e10db4d0726e75762f32.webm?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/aa8662d32c64e10db4d0726e75762f32.mp4?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BEAT BOSSES</strong><br>The big bads present you with quirky mechanics you’ll have to figure out on the fly for victory, and reward you with special perks. <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/4992ce97d2f44c5d7e89183cd5d3cf8a.poster.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/4992ce97d2f44c5d7e89183cd5d3cf8a.webm?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/4992ce97d2f44c5d7e89183cd5d3cf8a.mp4?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EARN NEW SHIPS</strong><br>Survive bosses to earn a whopping ten modes that change the gameplay. Make your runs easier, harder, or just plain weird.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/bc68850555d20e13c541b3673d983644.poster.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/bc68850555d20e13c541b3673d983644.webm?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/bc68850555d20e13c541b3673d983644.mp4?t=1759986058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PLAY WITH FRIENDS</strong><br>Invite your closest friends to challenge any game mode in a side by side co-op frenzy of fun. Share a couch, or use Steam's Remote Play to play with friends online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614790/extras/c7dd3b60e3df1fda55e6ae8a6ec8ddb1.avif?t=1759986058\" width=910 height=512 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLIMB THE LEADER BOARD</strong><br>Compete against the world's best GunDeck[100] players in a race to the furthest infinity level, using the least ammount of resources.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
